<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Hukdampa ei pui din A nai zing,
 Thil bangcheng hung tung mahleh ka bit hi;
 Guohpi, huihpi lakah ei sel ina,

[V2]
 A khut laivel nuom sung ah!
 A khut laivel nuom sung ah,
 A khut laivel nuom sung ah;
 Thil bangcheng hung tung mahleh ka bit hi,
 A khut laivel nuom sung ah!

[V3]
 2. A hehpihna ban sunga chun ei pawm,
 Lungmuonna thu haw chuh kei ei hilh tai;
 Pathien ngei chun ei ven ziekin ka bit,
 A khut laivel nuom sung ah.

[V4]
 3. Ka thagau vengin taihsan ngei puona,
 A hehpih apat ei khen thei umlo;
 Aman ei vawp zing ina tih ka hei,
 A khut laivel nuom sung ah.</lyrics>
<title>THE HOLLOW OF GOD'S HAND</title>
</song>